title: Laurika Rauch   -   2 Albums
description:
Laurika Rauch (born 1 November 1950 in Cape Town) is a South African singer who sings in the Afrikaans as well as English language. She had a hit single in 1979 with Kinders van die Wind, written by Koos du Plessis.
 
Including compilations of her greatest hits, Rauch has released 22 albums.
